library(dplyr) library(tidyr) library(shiny) library(shinymanager) library(ECharts2Shiny) library(shinyWidgets) table_options <- function() { list( dom = 'Bfrtip', pageLength = 10, buttons = list( c('copy', 'csv', 'excel', 'pdf', 'print'), list( extend = "collection", text = 'Show All', action = DT::JS( "function ( e, dt, node, config ) { dt.page.len(-1); dt.ajax.reload();}" ) ), list( extend = "collection", text = 'Show Less', action = DT::JS( "function ( e, dt, node, config ) { dt.page.len(10); dt.ajax.reload();}" ) ) ), deferRender = TRUE, lengthMenu = list(c(10, 20,-1), c('10', '20', 'All')), searching = FALSE, editable = TRUE, scroller = TRUE, lengthChange = FALSE , initComplete = DT::JS( "function(settings, json) {", "$(this.api().table().header()).css({'background-color': 'black', 'color': '#fff', 'font-size': '15px', 'text-align':'center'});","$(this.api().table().body()).css({'background-color': '#fff', 'color': 'black', 'font-size': '15px', 'text-align':'center'});", "}" ) ) } # dados <- read.csv2("SAR23Outubro2023.csv",header = T, sep = ",") dados <- read.csv2("ssar023A-2022.csv",header = T, sep = ",") mga <- subset(dados, subset = dados$campus == "MARINGA") ################################################################################ # *** Matriculados por Bloco - Geral *** Geral <- mga %>% group_by(bloco) %>% summarise("Vagas"=sum(vaga, na.rm = T), "Matriculados"=sum(mat, na.rm = T)) geral <- data.frame("Bloco"=Geral$bloco, "Vagas"=Geral$Vagas,"Matriculados" = Geral$Matriculados) row.names(geral) <- Geral$bloco geral <- geral[order(geral$Vagas, decreasing = TRUE),] ################################################################################ # *** Matriculados por Bloco/sala - Geral *** Sala <- mga %>% group_by(bloco,sala) %>% summarise("Vagas"=sum(vaga, na.rm = T), "Matriculados"=sum(mat, na.rm = T)) Sala <- as.data.frame(Sala[order(Sala$Vagas, decreasing = TRUE),]) colnames(Sala) <- c("bloco", "Sala", "Vagas", "Matriculados") ################################################################################ # *** Matriculados por semestre *** Per <- mga %>% group_by(bloco,sala,semestre) %>% summarise("Vagas"=sum(vaga, na.rm = T), "Matriculados"=sum(mat, na.rm = T)) Per <- Per %>% pivot_wider(names_from = semestre, values_from = c(Vagas,Matriculados), values_fill = 0) Per <- as.data.frame(Per[order(Per$Vagas_S1, decreasing = TRUE),]) PerT <- data.frame("Bloco"=Per$bloco,"Sala"=Per$sala, "Vagas A"=Per$`Vagas_A `, "Vagas S1"=Per$Vagas_S1, "Vagas S2" = Per$Vagas_S2, "Vagas Outros" = rowSums(Per[,6:14]), "Matriculados A" = Per$`Matriculados_A `, "Matriculados S1" = Per$Matriculados_S1, "Matriculados S2" = Per$Matriculados_S2, "Matriculados Outros" = rowSums(Per[,18:26])) ################################################################################ # *** Matriculados por semana *** # mga$dia <- case_when( mga$dia == 2 ~ "Seg", mga$dia == 3 ~ "Ter", mga$dia == 4 ~ "Qua", mga$dia == 5 ~ "Qui", mga$dia == 6 ~ "Sex", mga$dia == 7 ~ "Sab" ) sem <- mga %>% group_by(bloco,sala,dia) %>% summarise("Vagas"=sum(vaga, na.rm = T), "Matriculados"=sum(mat, na.rm = T)) sem <- sem %>% pivot_wider(names_from = dia, values_from = c(Vagas,Matriculados), values_fill = 0) sem <- as.data.frame(sem[order(sem$Vagas_Seg, decreasing = TRUE),]) ################################################################################ # *** Matriculados por semestre *** turno <- mga %>% group_by(bloco,sala,dia,aula) %>% summarise("Vagas"=sum(vaga, na.rm = T), "Matriculados"=sum(mat, na.rm = T)) # Matutino # Matutino 1° período Matutino1 <- turno[turno$aula <= 2,] %>% pivot_wider(names_from = dia, values_from = c(Vagas,Matriculados), values_fill = 0) Matutino1 <- aggregate(. ~ sala + bloco,data = Matutino1, sum) Matutino1 <- as.data.frame(Matutino1[order(Matutino1$sala, decreasing = F),]) # Matutino 2° período Matutino2 <- turno[turno$aula > 2 & turno$aula <= 4,] %>% pivot_wider(names_from = dia, values_from = c(Vagas,Matriculados), values_fill = 0) Matutino2 <- aggregate(. ~ sala + bloco,data = Matutino2, sum) Matutino2 <- as.data.frame(Matutino2[order(Matutino2$sala, decreasing = F),]) ################################################################################ # Vespertino # Vespertino 1° período Vespertino1 <- turno[turno$aula > 4 & turno$aula <= 8,] %>% pivot_wider(names_from = dia, values_from = c(Vagas,Matriculados), values_fill = 0) Vespertino1 <- aggregate(. ~ sala + bloco,data = Vespertino1, sum) Vespertino1 <- as.data.frame(Vespertino1[order(Vespertino1$sala, decreasing = F),]) # Vespertino 2° período Vespertino2 <- turno[turno$aula > 8 & turno$aula <= 12,] %>% pivot_wider(names_from = dia, values_from = c(Vagas,Matriculados), values_fill = 0) Vespertino2 <- aggregate(. ~ sala + bloco,data = Vespertino2, sum) Vespertino2 <- as.data.frame(Vespertino2[order(Vespertino2$sala, decreasing = F),]) ################################################################################ # Noturno # Noturno 1° período Noturno1 <- turno[turno$aula > 12 & turno$aula <= 14,] %>% pivot_wider(names_from = dia, values_from = c(Vagas,Matriculados), values_fill = 0) Noturno1 <- aggregate(. ~ sala + bloco,data = Noturno1, sum) Noturno1 <- as.data.frame(Noturno1[order(Noturno1$sala, decreasing = F),]) # Noturno 2° período Noturno2 <- turno[turno$aula > 14,] %>% pivot_wider(names_from = dia, values_from = c(Vagas,Matriculados), values_fill = 0) Noturno2 <- aggregate(. ~ sala + bloco,data = Noturno2, sum) Noturno2 <- as.data.frame(Noturno2[order(Noturno2$sala, decreasing = F),]) ################################################################################ credentials <- data.frame( user = c("Diogo", "Márcio"), password = c("852", "123"), stringsAsFactors = FALSE ) ui <- fluidPage( includeCSS("style.css"), loadEChartsLibrary(), loadEChartsTheme('shine'), loadEChartsTheme('vintage'), loadEChartsTheme('dark-digerati'), loadEChartsTheme('roma'), loadEChartsTheme('infographic'), loadEChartsTheme('macarons'), loadEChartsTheme('caravan'), loadEChartsTheme('jazz'), loadEChartsTheme('london'), navbarPage(title = "Fluxo - UEM - 2023", tabPanel("Geral", fluidRow( column(12,selectInput(inputId = 'xcol', label = 'Bloco', selected = "Total", choices = c("Total",Geral$bloco)) )), fluidPage( column(9, tags$div(id="geral",style="width:100%;height:500%;"), deliverChart(div_id = "geral"), HTML("
